                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370227-728-offence-1 t18370227-cd-27"></join>6th of February</rs>, at <placeName id="t18370227-geo-5">
                        <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370227-728-offence-1 t18370227-geo-5"></join>St.George, Hanover-square</placeName>, with intent to steal, and stealing therein, 12 yards of woollen cloth, value 12<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370227-name-359" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18370227-name-359" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
